blojsom 1.0 README
------------------

Developed with:
---------------
IntelliJ IDEA (http://www.intellij.net)

Tested under:
-------------
Jakarta Tomcat 4.1.18
Java 2 SDK 1.4.1
Mozilla 1.2.1
Mac OS X

Libraries
---------
The following libraries are required to compile and run blojsom. If you are using different versions of these APIs than those given here, you are on your own.

Servlet 2.2 API 
---------------
- Download from http://java.sun.com
- Place servlet-2.2b.jar file in /lib

Jakarta Commons Collections 2.1 API
-----------------------------------
- Download from http://jakarta.apache.org
- Place commons-collections-2.1.jar in war/WEB-INF/lib

Jakarta Commons Logging 1.0.2 API
---------------------------------
- Download from http://jakarta.apache.org
- Place commons-logging-1.0.2.jar in war/WEB-INF/lib

Jakarta Log4J 1.2.7 API
-----------------------
- Download from http://jakarta.apache.org
- Place log4j-1.2.7.jar in war/WEB-INF/lib

Velocity 1.3 API
----------------
- Download from http://jakarta.apache.org
- Place velocity-1.3.jar in war/WEB-INF/lib

Xerces 1.4.4 API
----------------
- Download from http://xml.apache.org
- Place xerces-1.4.4.jar in war/WEB-INF/lib

